{
  "chapter": 36,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为谢晓峰生命倒计时的哲学思辨。简传学诊断谢晓峰身中化骨散之毒，与金创药配合使用后创毒入骨，最多只能再活七天，最少三天。面对死亡，谢晓峰反而洒脱大笑，与众宾客饮酒畅谈\"如果只能活三天会做什么\"。施经墨坦言想杀人复仇，简传学坦白想放纵享乐，俏娘姨芳梅想嫁人再做寡妇。谢晓峰当场认芳梅为义妹，将她许配给丑医于俊才，并自报家门\"翠云峰绿水湖神剑山庄谢家三少爷\"。最后谢晓峰试探施经墨的心事，暗示\"有时用笔也一样能杀人的\"，为后续复仇埋下伏笔。本章以生死为引，揭示人性深处被礼教压抑的真实欲望。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这绝不是一点轻伤，那位先生伤势之重，学生至今还没有看见过。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你是什么东西？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "学生不是东西，学生是人，叫简传学。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你就是简复生的儿子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你既叫简传学，想必已传了他的医学，学问想必也不小。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "学生虽然才疏学浅，有关刀圭金创这方面的医理，倒也还知道一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些叔叔伯伯，也都是个中老手，我等治不好的伤，别人想必也治不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你怎么知道别人也治不好？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 21,
      "line_end": 23
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那位先生身上的伤，一共有五处，两处是旧创，三处是这两天才被人用利剑刺伤的，虽然不在要害上，可是每一剑都刺得很深，已伤及关节处的筋骨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "病人受了伤之后，若是立刻求医疗养，也许还有救，可惜他受伤后又劳动过度，而且还喝了酒，喝的又太多，伤口已经开始在溃烂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是严重的，还是那两处旧创，就算我们能把新伤治好，他也只能再活七天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "七天？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "最多七天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "可是那两处旧创看起来岂非早已收了口？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "就因为创痕已经收了口，所以最多只能再活七天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "我不懂！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "你当然不会懂，懂得这种事的人本就不多，不幸他却偏偏认得一个，而且恰巧是他的朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "是他的朋友？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他受伤之后，就恰巧遇见了这位朋友，这位朋友身上，恰巧带着最好的金创药，又恰巧带着最毒的化骨散。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "金创药生肌，化骨散蚀骨，剑痕收口时，创毒已入骨，七天之内，他的全身一百三十七根骨骼，都必将化为脓血。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "没有药可以解这种毒？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "没有！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "也没有人可以解这种毒？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xiao_di",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "最多七天，最少几天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "三天。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你为什么还要笑？你怎么还能笑得出？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大家远路而来，主人难道连酒都不招待？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你常喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我常喝，可是喝得不多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "如果一个人常喝酒，是不是因为他喜欢喝？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "大概是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "既然喜欢喝，为什么不多喝些？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为喝太多总是对身体有损，所以……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "所以你心里虽然想喝，却不得不勉强控制自己。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "因为你还想活下去，还想多活几年，活得越久越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "每个人活着时，都一定有很多心里很想去做，却不敢去做的事，因为一个人只要想活下去，就难免会有很多拘束，很多顾忌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "巴巴众生中，又有谁能无拘无束，随心所欲！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "有一种人！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪种？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "知道自己最多只能再活几天的人。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果你知道你自己最多只能再活几天，在这几天里，你会做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "speaker_name": "施经墨",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果是我，我会杀人！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "你要去杀人？杀多少人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "speaker_name": "施经墨",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "杀多少人？我能杀多少人？",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "你想杀多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "speaker_name": "施经墨",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我本来只想杀一个的，现在想想，还有两个也一样该死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "他们都很对不起你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "只可惜你还有许多日子可以活，所以你也只有眼看着他们逍遥自在的活下去，很可能活得比你还陕活。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "speaker_name": "施经墨",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不错，就因为我还可以活下去，所以也只有让他们活下去。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你是个很有才能的人，出身好，学问好，而且刚强正直，想必一直都受人尊敬，你自己当然也不敢做出一点超越规矩礼教的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "可是如果你只能活三天，你会去干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我……我会去好好的安排后事，然后静静的等死。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不是真话，完全不是。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果我只能再活三天，我会去大吃大喝，狂嫖烂赌，把全城的婊子都找来，脱光了跟她们捉迷藏。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_fu_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "简复生",
      "listener": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "text": "你……你怎么会想到要做这种事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这种事本来就很有趣，如果你只能活三天，你说不定也会去做的！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我……我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜你们都还要活很久，所以你们心里就算想得要命，也只能偷偷的在心里想想而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jian_chuan_xue",
      "speaker_name": "简传学",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老实说，我简直连想都不敢想。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_fang_mei",
      "text": "如果你只能活三天了，你想干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_di",
      "speaker_name": "小弟",
      "listener": "char_fang_mei",
      "text": "谢先生既然在问你，你就要说老实话。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我想嫁人。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_fang_mei",
      "text": "你一直都没有嫁！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_fang_mei",
      "text": "为什么不嫁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我从小就被卖给人家做丫环，能嫁给什么样的男人？有什么样的男人肯娶我？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_fang_mei",
      "text": "可是你若只能活三天，就不管什么样的人都要嫁！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "只要男人就行，只要是活男人就行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "然后我就杀了他。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既然已经嫁给了他，为什么又要杀了他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我没有做过寡妇，我还想尝尝做寡妇是什么滋味。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜我还不会死，所以我非但做不了寡妇，还很可能连嫁都嫁不出去。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_jun_cai",
      "speaker_name": "于俊才",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如果我只能活三天，我一定娶她。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yu_jun_cai",
      "text": "你真的想娶她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_jun_cai",
      "speaker_name": "于俊才",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这女人又干净，又标致，能娶到这样的老婆，已经算是福气，只可惜……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yu_jun_cai",
      "text": "只可惜你既然还不会死，就得顾全你们家的面子，总不能把个丫头用八人大轿娶回去。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "刚才你们都想问我，一个明知道自己快要死了的人，怎么还能笑得出？现在你们为什么不问了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为现在你们心里都在偷偷的羡慕我，因为你们心里想做，却不敢去做的事，我都可以去做。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_jun_cai",
      "speaker_name": "于俊才",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你呢？在这三天里，你想干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yu_jun_cai",
      "text": "我要你娶她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_jun_cai",
      "speaker_name": "于俊才",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "娶谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yu_jun_cai",
      "text": "我义妹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_jun_cai",
      "speaker_name": "于俊才",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你义妹？谁是你义妹？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我的义妹就是她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_fang_mei",
      "text": "你姓什么，叫什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "做丫头的还有什么姓，主人替我取了个名字，叫芳梅，我就叫芳梅！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_fang_mei",
      "text": "现在你已有了姓，姓谢！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "姓谢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_fang_mei",
      "text": "现在你是我的义妹，我姓谢，你不姓谢姓什么！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是你……你……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 317,
      "line_end": 317
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我就是翠云峰，绿水湖，神剑山庄，谢家的三少爷谢晓峰。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_mei",
      "speaker_name": "芳梅",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "谢家的三少爷？谢晓峰？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不管谁做了谢家三少爷的义妹，都绝对不是件丢人的事！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在我宣布你们已经成夫妇，有没有人反对？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "那个人是你的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "speaker_name": "施经墨",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 339,
      "line_end": 339
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "对不起你的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 341,
      "line_end": 341
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "speaker_name": "施经墨",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我……我一直都拿他当朋友，可是他……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "他做了什么对不起你的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "我看得出你是个老实人。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "speaker_name": "施经墨",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我只不过是个没有用的人。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "可是你至少读过书。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "speaker_name": "施经墨",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "也许就因为我读过书，所以才会变得如此无用！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "有用。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "speaker_name": "施经墨",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "有用？有什么用？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_jing_mo",
      "text": "有时用笔也一样能杀人的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 36,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    }
